HOW TO SETUP YOUR LIFEBOTS BOT

Setting up your LifeBots bot is quick and easy! Just follow the steps below:

   You need a LifeBots account. If you don’t already have one, create one at https://lifebots.cloud/auth/register
   Login to your LifeBots account.
   Go to the Dashboard.
   If it’s your first bot, click “Add your first Bot Now!”. Otherwise, click the “Add Bot” button.
   Enter the Username and Password for the bot (use the same password you would use in the Second Life viewer).
   Select Bot Type (Full or Lite Bot). See Related Article
   Add the bot.
   Pay for the bot.

Done 🎉 Your bot is now ready!

